[H1]Dependency Selection:

[H2]ROCm
  Enabled/Disable ROCm required dependencies for display/validate/install.

[H2]Driver
  Enabled/Disable amdgpu Driver required dependencies for
  display/validate/install.

[H1]Dependency Management:

[H2]Display Dependencies
  Display a list of all 1st-level dependencies required for ROCm/amdgpu
  functionality.

[H2]Validate Dependencies
  Validate the currently installed 1st-level dependencies for ROCm/amdgpu
  on the system.

[H2]Install Dependencies
  Install 1st-level dependencies required for ROCm/amdgpu on the system.
